% layout 'default';
% title 'Lang | About';

<h2><%= $msg; %></h2>
<p>lang is a basic flashcard system. Features include:</p>

<ul class="lang-list">
	<li>translation in multiple representations (greek/cyrillic/hebrew/arabic/etc and transliteration)</li>
	<li>login with email/password</li>
	<li>create lists and flashcards</li>
	<li>mark success/fail</li>
	<li>select flat, random, or success-modified card frequency</li>
</ul>
